TopicTitle: Your most recent google search must fight the last persons google search

Articles.Content:
Its simple what you last googled must fight what the last person searched.

Ottoman Empire, powerful nation that lasted 500 years
Team Fortress 2. I called nine mercenaries to kill you.
Grand admiral Thrawn i bombard your mercenaries from orbit with the imperial navy
Nuke. I nuke you.
Alan Becker's AVM  (Animation vs. Minecraft).     I infiltrate your computer and take it over so you can never launch the nuke!
Chey-Tac Intervention M200. I 360 No Scoped Alan Becker so there's no AVM anymore.
76.2 mm L-11 cannon commonly fitted on KV-1 (L-11) and 1940s era T-34 Soviet tanks. My 7.6cm solid shot rounds shall cause your puny Western sniper rifle to simply cease to exist.
Captain America: The first avenger. I call a bunch of hi-tech Hydra army to destroy the tank.
RD-251: A rocket engine. Stands no chance.

A cat jumping from a cucumber.

It jumps directly into the rocket engine (rip el gato) and blocks the engine bell and causes the gas inside the rocket engine to explode under the unbearable pressure.

How to get carrots in Minecraft.

The cat investigates the carrots.

Spam monty python

Carrots and cats don't like spam!

Fun Swedish words/Swedish to English

I wonder if morötter och katter like tjugosju svenska stjärnor while driving lastbilar in blåsväder over a farthinder on their way to Södertälje delivering Spam. I don't think the katter liked it. Där, är du glad nu?

I wonder if carrots and cats like twenty-seven Swedish stars while driving trucks in windy weather over a speedbump on their way to Södertälje delivering Spam. I don't think the cats liked it. There, are you happy now?

A DAF XF105 driving 20 km/h over the speed limit drives over a car half stuck in the road, flies into the air, hits a Scania S that was also flying through the air after driving over a truck's trailer that was half stuck in the road and slanted like a ramp, explodes, and destroys all the moderators. Haha, lastbilar go boom.

Lastbil is truck, by the way. Lastbilar is the plural form of that, trucks.

History, I use all of the military’s ever used and attack this town

DAF XG+ review. I'm not really sure how a Dutch truck can fight against history...

Oh wait, I'm in Eindhoven, The Netherlands, not Lahich, Azerbaijan! All of the military from history attacks Lahich while I sit on a comfortable 800 millimetre wide bed at in the back of a truck 4,295.8 km away, on the KSP forums.

D-DAY, the invasion is redirected from Normandy to the Netherlands instead in order to take out the strategic objective of the DAF XG+.

A German DAF XG+ battalion puts up staunch resistance, but it cannot hope to hold out for too long.
